  "title": "[FIRRTL] Runtime overhead for NLA verification",
  "body": "We should look at opportunity to reduce the runtime overhead for NLA verification.\r\nFor example, `PrefixModules` pass takes `10` seconds with NLA verification and `6` without it.\r\nThe only difference between the following two runs is the NLA verification commit:https://github.com/llvm/circt/commit/e11364bd88578655e60cc98c001c7a3915dd6936\r\nHere's the `FIRRTL` timings (release build) with the `NLA` verification on an internal testcase (P550)\r\n```\r\n===-------------------------------------------------------------------------===\r\n                         ... Execution time report ...\r\n===-------------------------------------------------------------------------===\r\n  Total Execution Time: 268.8243 seconds\r\n\r\n  ----User Time----  ----Wall Time----  ----Name----\r\n   36.1850 (  6.8%)   36.1850 ( 13.5%)  FIR Parser\r\n  460.0650 ( 86.2%)  195.2862 ( 72.6%)  'firrtl.circuit' Pipeline\r\n   62.3900 ( 11.7%)    3.6809 (  1.4%)    'firrtl.module' Pipeline\r\n   58.0054 ( 10.9%)    3.4350 (  1.3%)      CSE\r\n    0.1572 (  0.0%)    0.0223 (  0.0%)        (A) DominanceInfo\r\n    4.2245 (  0.8%)    0.3223 (  0.1%)      LowerCHIRRTLPass\r\n   14.5737 (  2.7%)   14.5737 (  5.4%)    InferWidths\r\n   15.9479 (  3.0%)   15.9479 (  5.9%)    InferResets\r\n    0.5856 (  0.1%)    0.5856 (  0.2%)      (A) circt::firrtl::InstanceGraph\r\n    4.7727 (  0.9%)    4.7727 (  1.8%)    WireDFT\r\n   10.2660 (  1.9%)   10.2660 (  3.8%)    PrefixModules\r\n   17.8434 (  3.3%)   17.8434 (  6.6%)    LowerFIRRTLTypes\r\n  164.4766 ( 30.8%)   14.9738 (  5.6%)    'firrtl.module' Pipeline\r\n   27.9946 (  5.2%)    1.7767 (  0.7%)      ExpandWhens\r\n    0.2770 (  0.1%)    0.1259 (  0.0%)      RemoveResets\r\n  125.3170 ( 23.5%)   12.3260 (  4.6%)      Canonicalizer\r\n   10.8369 (  2.0%)    0.8750 (  0.3%)      InferReadWrite\r\n   12.0843 (  2.3%)   12.0843 (  4.5%)    Inliner\r\n   15.9953 (  3.0%)   15.9953 (  6.0%)    IMConstProp\r\n    0.4122 (  0.1%)    0.4122 (  0.2%)      (A) circt::firrtl::InstanceGraph\r\n    6.5786 (  1.2%)    6.5786 (  2.4%)    BlackBoxReader\r\n   48.5673 (  9.1%)   48.5673 ( 18.1%)    GrandCentral\r\n    0.3644 (  0.1%)    0.3644 (  0.1%)      (A) circt::firrtl::InstanceGraph\r\n    7.0181 (  1.3%)    7.0181 (  2.6%)    GrandCentralTaps\r\n    0.4083 (  0.1%)    0.4083 (  0.2%)      (A) circt::firrtl::InstanceGraph\r\n   42.9835 (  8.1%)    7.1086 (  2.6%)    'firrtl.module' Pipeline\r\n    0.1216 (  0.0%)    0.0290 (  0.0%)      GrandCentralSignalMappings\r\n   42.5866 (  8.0%)    7.1055 (  2.6%)      Canonicalizer\r\n    5.7920 (  1.1%)    5.7920 (  2.2%)    RemoveUnusedPorts\r\n    0.3706 (  0.1%)    0.3706 (  0.1%)      (A) circt::firrtl::InstanceGraph\r\n    3.6014 (  0.7%)    3.6014 (  1.3%)    CreateSiFiveMetadata\r\n    0.3211 (  0.1%)    0.3211 (  0.1%)      (A) circt::firrtl::InstanceGraph\r\n    6.4564 (  1.2%)    6.4564 (  2.4%)    EmitOMIR\r\n   37.0020 (  6.9%)   37.0020 ( 13.8%)  Print .mlir output\r\n    0.3487 (  0.1%)    0.3487 (  0.1%)  Rest\r\n  533.6030 (100.0%)  268.8243 (100.0%)  Total\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd the timings without the NLA verification commit, \r\n```\r\n===-------------------------------------------------------------------------===\r\n                         ... Execution time report ...\r\n===-------------------------------------------------------------------------===\r\n  Total Execution Time: 235.7990 seconds\r\n\r\n  ----User Time----  ----Wall Time----  ----Name----\r\n   32.5676 (  6.4%)   32.5676 ( 13.8%)  FIR Parser\r\n  434.3394 ( 85.6%)  162.9016 ( 69.1%)  'firrtl.circuit' Pipeline\r\n   60.6479 ( 12.0%)    3.7544 (  1.6%)    'firrtl.module' Pipeline\r\n   56.5306 ( 11.1%)    3.6028 (  1.5%)      CSE\r\n    0.1271 (  0.0%)    0.0193 (  0.0%)        (A) DominanceInfo\r\n    3.9916 (  0.8%)    0.3067 (  0.1%)      LowerCHIRRTLPass\r\n   10.0561 (  2.0%)   10.0561 (  4.3%)    InferWidths\r\n   11.8735 (  2.3%)   11.8735 (  5.0%)    InferResets\r\n    0.5926 (  0.1